- act availability: not installed locally (fallback to direct local validation)
- Local validation executed:
  - python scripts/phase5_geometric_solution.py
  - python scripts/stability_audit_ch01_ch03.py
  - pytest -q tests/test_stability_audit_regression.py tests/test_canonical_asset_paths.py tests/test_phase4_zenodo_package.py tests/test_phase5_geometric_solution.py

